    "get_face_model_coefficients": "x.get_face_model_coefficients(character) -> Array[float]\r\n\r\nbrief: Gets the coefficients of the underlying face model for the given character. Requires the character to be added for edit using TryAddObjectToEdit\r\n\r\nArgs:\r\n    character (MetaHumanCharacter): The character to obtain the coefficients for\r\n\r\nReturns:\r\n    Array[float]: \r\n\r\n    out_coefficients (Array[float]): The coefficients array to fill",
    "set_face_model_coefficients": "x.set_face_model_coefficients(character, coefficients) -> None\r\n\r\nbrief: Sets the coefficients of the underlying face model for the given character. Requires the character to be added for edit using TryAddObjectToEdit\r\n\r\nArgs:\r\n    character (MetaHumanCharacter): The character to update\r\n    coefficients (Array[float]): The coefficients to apply",
    "compare_face_state": "x.compare_face_state(character1, character2, tolerance) -> bool\r\nEvaluate the face state for each of the supplied characters, and compare the vertices and vertex normals\nRequires the characters to have been added for edit using TryAddObjectToEdit\nReturns true if all corresponding vertices and vertex normals are within InTolerance of each other in terms of vector norm\r\n\r\nArgs:\r\n    character1 (MetaHumanCharacter): \r\n    character2 (MetaHumanCharacter): \r\n    tolerance (float): \r\n\r\nReturns:\r\n    bool:",
    "commit_face_state": "x.commit_face_state(character) -> None\r\nCommits the Face State of the given Character to be serialized. This needs to be done after after using the\nsculpting or blending APIs to persist the changes\nRequires the character to be added for edit using TryAddObjectToEdit\r\n\r\nArgs:\r\n    character (MetaHumanCharacter):",
    "commit_body_state": "x.commit_body_state(character) -> None\r\nCommits the Body State of the given Character to be serialized. This needs to be done after after using the\nsculpting or blending APIs to persist the changes\nRequires the character to be added for edit using TryAddObjectToEdit\r\n\r\nArgs:\r\n    character (MetaHumanCharacter):",
